Subtitle File Format Specifications
===================================

  The subtitle file format specifications stored in this directory are by no
  means official. Most of them are gathered from various unofficial sources as
  no official specification has been found. MicroDVD specification is the only
  one that looks thorough and insighful.

  Sources have not been listed for all information, as I haven't found the web
  sites anymore. The main reason to have these files here is because web pages
  tend to vanish or change hosting.
